Package interfaces

Interface Subject

All Known Implementing Classes:
Broker
public interface Subject
Subject interface, that can notify observers of the events happened in the auction

  • Method Summary

    Modifier and Type Method Description
    void add​(Observer o)
    Adds an observer to the subscribers list
    void notifyObserver​(Observer o, double bid)
    Notifies a specific observer about the maximum bid after a specific step
    void notifyObservers​(double bid, Product demandedProduct)
    Notifies the observers about the maximum bid of the demanded product
    void removeObserver​(Observer o)
    Removes an Observer from the list

  • Method Details

    • add

      void add​(Observer o)
      Adds an observer to the subscribers list
      Parameters:
      o - the added observer

    • notifyObservers

      void notifyObservers​(double bid, Product demandedProduct)
      Notifies the observers about the maximum bid of the demanded product
      Parameters:
      bid - the maximum bid in the current step of an auction
      demandedProduct - the product demanded by the observers

    • notifyObserver

      void notifyObserver​(Observer o, double bid)
      Notifies a specific observer about the maximum bid after a specific step
      Parameters:
      o - the Observer to be notified
      bid - the maximum bid in the current step of an auction

    • removeObserver

      void removeObserver​(Observer o)
      Removes an Observer from the list
      Parameters:
      o - the Observer to be removed
